      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine without a single scratch, swirl, or stone chip. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with supple leather and every feature functioning exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is in perfect order, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards.",
