      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an impeccable standard that defies its pre-owned status. This unit exhibits a showroom-quality aesthetic, free from any visual or mechanical imperfections. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our highest benchmarks for performance and luxury. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine specimen.",
